DescDetail: <<
OpenVRML is a portable toolkit including a C++ library for reading
and displaying VRML and X3D files, an OpenGL renderer, and a Mozilla
Web browser plug-in for viewing VRML and X3D content on the Internet.

This version of the package will build without script node javascript
support or the Mozilla plugin on Intel. This will be added in a later
version.
<<
DescPort: <<
Uses X11 to satisfy fontconfig and freetype dependencies.
Uses zlib from OS X.
<<
DescPackaging: <<
At present, does not build Mozilla plugin or Javascript support
on Intel Mac OS X, because Mozilla is PPC-only, and support for
Seamonkey or Firefox is not yet present in the source.
<<
Homepage: http://www.openvrml.org/
